        <div xml:id="cice-l5t15-Dd1e108">
          <head xml:id="cice-l5t15-Hd1e110">CAP. UN.</head>
          <p xml:id="cice-l5t15-d1e113">Excommunicandus est sagittarius et ballistarius contra Christianos. Hoc dicit.</p>
          <p xml:id="cice-l5t15-d1e116">Innocentius III.</p>
          <p xml:id="cice-l5t15-d1e119">Artem autem illam mortiferam et [Deo] odibilem ballistariorum et sagittariorum adversus
            Christianos et catholicos exerceri de cetero sub anathemate prohibemus.</p>
